posts.title: A warning to the USA about Indians, from a friend across the pond (UK)
posts.content:
I've been watching with HORROR at what Elon has been saying. It's clear (to me) as a non-American, what you're about to experience. You may or may not believe me. You might say I'm wrong. You might say "that'll never happen in the USA!!!" yeah......that's what we said too here in the UK.

I want to give you guys a visual on what Indian people are like. What their culture is. And then how the USA will look once Indian's flood you, like they've done here.

  1. Drinking cow shit and cow piss - https://youtu.be/RuM6aXcNdyQ?si=2wEMikTFjnTMagBo (they see cows as a "god"). This is the least disgusting video you'll see. There are videos of them eating cow shit from a wrap (I kid you not)

  2. Hygiene - or lack thereof - https://www.youtube.com/shorts/Vy9lR5WIAGM - Indian hygiene is non-existent. They'll literally go for a shit, wipe their hands on their junk and serve you up a slop of food on a leaf. They'll open up restaurants in the USA and they'll have rat droppings and off-meat which you'll be served under a veil of sauce to mask the taste

  3. Spit and shit and other human waste - https://youtube.com/shorts/ot9PbkV1Dwk?si=v4spV5pKaCNPr51J - Indians will LITERALLY take a shit in the street if they need to go. Toilet? Wtf is a toilet. Who needs one of those when you can shit in the streets.

  4. Hygiene again - they'll literally use any part of their body, in this case, their armpit to help them prepare food - https://youtube.com/shorts/ot9PbkV1Dwk?si=v4spV5pKaCNPr51J

  5. Indians will shit on a beach - literally, take dumps on your local beautiful beach - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Trga0KMcn4

  6. Manners - India doesn't know what manners are. They'll overcrowd a train and push you off whilst the train is going full speed if you're in their way - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_BXkHjTAQe4

If you're still not getting it.... or thinking I'm being overly pessimistic, or thinking: "yeah right, what does this British guy know????" , let another British guy show you India. Watch the whole video to gain an understanding:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IFUIdcrgW6M

Take it from a guy who has had the UK flooded with people we were told would be "doctors", "engineers" and "highly educated" people with 3rd world immigrants. YOU DO NOT WANT THEM. This is not a racist thing - this is a fact. You do NOT want these people to ruin the USA.

Give it 5-10 years of immigration the USA will resemble India, mark my words

From a friendly British guy over the pond :-)
